title: VANS CABINET SHOP is taking applications for a cabinet
text:
VANS CABINET SHOP is taking applications for a cabinet ad date: 10/17/2015 
VANS CABINET SHOP is taking applications for a cabinet shop position; pay DOE. A F/T position with benefits avail. Job duties: finishing out cabinets; setting drawers; installing cabinet doors; misc cabinet duties. Apply in person at 20053 Hwy 108 Sonora.
